{
  "id": "adv_main_01_05_03",
  "title": "星見編1章24話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ここに入ることは出来ますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can I join your agency?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "私、高校のダンス大会では優勝しています\n芸能活動に役立つとは思いますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve won a high school dance championship.\nI believe it will help in my endeavors as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.411655518909296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "本当に！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.60621337890625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.215306329727174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "高校のダンス大会で優勝しているんだよ\nきっといろんなこと教えてもらったり、吸収できる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s a high school dance champion.\nI’m sure there’s a lot we can learn from her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.44297069708507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。みんなが良ければ、怜を新メンバーとして\n迎え入れるよう、事務所に話してみる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. If everyone’s okay with it‚ I’ll talk to the agency\nand see if we can welcome Rei in as a new member.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.642970697085072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……一ノ瀬さ……いや、怜もそれでいいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ichinose-sa… sorry‚ Rei‚ are you okay with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.469818568229684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。それを仕事として、職業として\n両親に紹介出来るのであれば、私は構いません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. As long as I can tell my parents\nit’s a job‚ a career‚ I’m fine with that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.95526060263316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 43.388593935966476
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 43.75526060263316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあそのNEXT VENUSグランプリというので\n頂点に立つのが、当面の目標になる訳ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me get this right. So your current goal\nis to make it to the top of this NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.58859393596648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？\nああ、まあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?\nUm‚ well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.63694865703581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "違うんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that not the case?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.212662887573224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "実はまだ決めてないの\n出場するかしないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ we still haven’t decided\nwhether or not we’re going to enter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.44309376875559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "May I ask why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6037514925003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "………………それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.13708482583363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……そんなに簡単じゃないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Because it’s not that simple.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.23708482583362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "エントリーしなければ\nいつまでたっても難しいままじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you don’t enter‚\nit’ll always remain that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2370848258336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "少なくとも私は出ます\n始める以上、結果を残さないと気が済まないので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In any case‚ I’ll be entering.\nIf I’m going to do this‚ I plan on delivering results.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.71826380888619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.81931394139923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……はっきりした方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We should decide.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0859806080659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.81931394139922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど五人\n多数決とれば、結論は出るわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are five of us.\nIf we vote on it‚ we’ll have a majority decision.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9246881028016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "では、決をとります\nNEXT VENUSグランプリに出たい人……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s take a vote.\nAll in favor of entering the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.02468810280156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（二人……今年は出ないという形になるのか……）\n（俺がそう思った時、遅れて一つの手が挙がった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Two of them… Looks like they won’t be entering this year.）\n（Just as I think that another hand slowly rises.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.72468810280152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 108.79135476946824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.41763631701457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "後悔……したくない……から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t wanna… regret…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.25096965034793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3509695549805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん達がグランプリに出て\nステージに立っているの見たら、きっと後悔する……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I see my sister and the others\nstanding on stage at the Grand Prix‚ I’m sure I’ll regret it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.88430288831394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリのステージも、お姉ちゃんも\nもっともっと遠くにいっちゃう……そんな気がする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like… I’ll become even more distant\nfrom the Grand Prix… and my sister…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.58758187492698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.22091520826032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　みんな集まって、やらない？\nアイドルがよくやってるヤツ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! How about we do that thing?\nThat thing idols always do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.08758187492697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "よくやってるヤツ……なんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What thing?",
        "id": ""
      },
